OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly morning mist and fog
OL,6,Fquickly clearing to leave a fine day
OL,7,Fwith patchy cloud and light winds.
OL,8,FFeeling warm or very warm in the
OL,9,Fsunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and fine end to the day
OL,12,Fwith plenty of evening sunshine.
OL,13,FStaying dry overnight with clear
OL,14,Fspells, some patchy cloud and light
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FContinuing largely fine, dry
OL,18,Fand settled, however skies turning a
OL,19,Flittle hazy at times. Still feeling
OL,20,Frather warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
